title: Flying Swords of Dragon Gate
description: A courtesan and a swordsman take refuge in the infamous Dragon Inn, as an explosive mix of warriors, fugitives and assassins converge for a deadly showdown. Starring international action legend, Jet Li. (2011)

title: Bronwyn Oliver: The Shadows Within
description: This intimate documentary follows the journey of Bronwyn Oliver, a working-class girl from the country who became one of Australia's most influential contemporary sculptors.
description2: This intimate documentary follows the journey of Bronwyn Oliver, a working-class girl from the country who became one of Australia's most influential contemporary sculptors.

title: Step Into Paradise
description: The extraordinary story of iconic fashion designers Jenny Kee and Linda Jackson, whose pioneering style created a bold and unashamedly Australian fashion identity. (2020)
description2: The extraordinary story of iconic fashion designers Jenny Kee and Linda Jackson, whose pioneering style created a bold and unashamedly Australian fashion identity.

title: Uncle Vanya
description: An adaptation of Anton Chekhov's masterpiece - a portrayal of life at the turn of the 20th century. Full of tumultuous frustration, dark humour and hidden passions, a conflicted family is forced to confront their despair.

title: Ties That Bind
description: 17 year-old Thomas has to front his domineering mother Marlene. Forced outside as punishment, sounds from neighbours echo a connection to his past and present home triggering Thomas to make a life changing decision.
